  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I find out that in-- in Lenin-- in the city-- this was, like, on the railroad, a little small town, but I went to the city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I find the out that the Polish-- like not embassy, but organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they have a school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I enter in that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I went there and talked to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they took me in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was like you slept there, and you ate, and you went to school and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was there for a little while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "How old were you at this time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "About?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me already that you cannot be much longer because until 18 years of age.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the men there [INAUDIBLE] says, how about you go learn a trade?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're going to teach you a trade, and you go out on your own and working.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he put me into the-- I wanted to go-- two choices he says you have.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're going to learn cinematography-- 'Kino' means movie, movie camera, you know in those days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Movie camera-- or you can be a truck driver.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, unfortunately, in those days, a truck driver was much more worth than cinematography.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wish I look cinematography at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did truck driving because truck driving, you made a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went to school there, and I finished the course there for a driver.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was driving like a second hel-- helper on a truck with somebody else with a man I know from Poland too, a Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I drove with him for a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I drove myself there for awhile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, I-- between time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] find out that my mom and my brother are in Asia, but far away there.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
